                     <interp inst="t18000917-54-person587" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a constable: I apprehended the prisoner on the 25th upon another charge; when I searched him, I found in his breeches four duplicates, one of which applied to this property.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. those are my sheets, they have my mark upon them.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I have nothing to say.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18000917-54-verdict293" type="verdictDescription">
